statements: SELECT * FROM telehealth_analytics
SELECT user_id, login_time, duration_minutes FROM telehealth_analytics WHERE call_quality_rating >= 3
SELECT user_id, session_id, device_type FROM telehealth_analytics ORDER BY login_time DESC
SELECT user_id, user_location FROM telehealth_analytics WHERE device_type = 'Mobile' LIMIT 10
SELECT AVG(duration_minutes) AS average_duration, MAX(call_quality_rating) AS max_rating FROM telehealth_analytics
SELECT user_id, session_id, login_time, duration_minutes, device_type, user_location, connection_speed, call_quality_rating FROM telehealth_analytics;
SELECT * FROM telehealth_analytics ORDER BY login_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, session_id, device_type FROM telehealth_analytics WHERE duration_minutes > 30;
SELECT user_location, AVG(call_quality_rating) AS avg_rating FROM telehealth_analytics GROUP BY user_location;
SELECT user_id, device_type, duration_minutes FROM telehealth_analytics WHERE connection_speed = 'High-speed' ORDER BY duration_minutes DESC;
SELECT * FROM appointments WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000';
SELECT appointment_id, appointment_date, appointment_time FROM appointments WHERE doctor_id = '234e5678-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000';
SELECT appointment_id, consultation_fee FROM appointments WHERE doctor_id = '345e6789-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000' ORDER BY appointment_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM rating_reviews WHERE rating >= 4;
SELECT review_text, rating FROM rating_reviews WHERE doctor_id = '456e7890-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000';
SELECT * FROM appointments WHERE appointment_date = '2023-04-15';
SELECT appointment_id, appointment_date, appointment_time, consultation_fee FROM appointments WHERE consultation_fee > 50 ORDER BY appointment_date ASC;
SELECT user_id, doctor_id, appointment_date, appointment_time FROM appointments WHERE doctor_id = '435e06b6-4b5c-4c8f-8234-1d0d4b62b1f4' AND appointment_date BETWEEN '2023-05-01' AND '2023-05-31';
SELECT * FROM rating_reviews WHERE rating > 3 AND review_text IS NOT NULL ORDER BY review_id DESC;

SELECT appointments.appointment_id, appointments.appointment_date, rating_reviews.rating, rating_reviews.review_text FROM appointments JOIN rating_reviews ON appointments.appointment_id = rating_reviews.appointment_id WHERE rating_reviews.rating = 5 ORDER BY appointment_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM telehealth_users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM telehealth_users;
SELECT appointment_id, appointment_date, doctor_name FROM telehealth_appointments;
SELECT user_id, appointment_date, consultation_fee FROM telehealth_appointments;
SELECT timestamp, metric_name, metric_value FROM telehealth_metrics;
SELECT * FROM telehealth_users WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY username DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, email FROM telehealth_users WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT username, email, age FROM telehealth_users WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 40 ORDER BY age ASC, username DESC;

SELECT appointment_id, appointment_date, doctor_name, appointment_type, consultation_fee FROM telehealth_appointments WHERE appointment_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY appointment_date ASC, consultation_fee DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT metric_id, timestamp, metric_name, metric_value FROM telehealth_metrics WHERE metric_value > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC, metric_value ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT provider_name, provider_specialty FROM Telehealth_Provider
SELECT provider_id, provider_name, provider_location, provider_specialty FROM Telehealth_Provider
SELECT provider_name, provider_specialty, provider_location FROM Telehealth_Provider ORDER BY provider_location DESC
SELECT * FROM Telehealth_Patient
SELECT * FROM Telehealth_Provider;
SELECT provider_name, provider_specialty FROM Telehealth_Provider ORDER BY provider_specialty ASC;
SELECT * FROM Telehealth_Patient WHERE patient_age > 30;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM Telehealth_Provider WHERE provider_specialty = 'Cardiology';
SELECT appointment_date, appointment_time FROM Telehealth_Appointment WHERE appointment_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT * FROM Procedure;
SELECT procedure_id, procedure_name, procedure_category FROM Procedure WHERE provider_id = 1;
SELECT patient_name, gender, date_of_birth FROM Patient ORDER BY date_of_birth DESC;
SELECT provider_name, specialization, address, contact_number FROM Provider WHERE specialization = 'Cardiology';
SELECT * FROM Appointments WHERE appointment_type = 'Follow-up' ORDER BY appointment_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM Procedure ORDER BY procedure_name DESC, date_performed ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT provider_name, specialization, address FROM Provider WHERE specialization='Cardiology' OR specialization='Dermatology';
SELECT appointment_id, appointment_date, appointment_type FROM Appointments WHERE appointment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY appointment_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT metric_name, metric_value, date_recorded FROM Metrics WHERE provider_id=3 ORDER BY date_recorded DESC LIMIT 10;
